    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867320/extras/9ae629892bd2d492a38a96cb3529b9f9.avif?t=1771010071\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867320/extras_big/9ae629892bd2d492a38a96cb3529b9f9.avif?t=1771010071 width=800 height=458 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\tWelcome to Werewolves Revenge, a <strong>first person social deduction game</strong> with over <strong>200 powerful roles</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867320/extras/5837029795cf0b0d4f22bd2753ec1536.avif?t=1771010071\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867320/extras_big/5837029795cf0b0d4f22bd2753ec1536.avif?t=1771010071 width=800 height=266 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867320/extras/f8c1f44289ab380f4480ca7ba618ffb0.webp?t=1771010071\" width=592 height=42 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\tUncover hidden roles and objectives through <strong>bluffing</strong>, <strong>strategic questioning</strong>, and <strong>keen observation</strong>. As the Town, vanquish all werewolves before it's too late. As the Werewolves, hunt down and meticulously kill the villagers one by one.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >‎ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >‎ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867320/extras/d8d2eaf43adbd2b921912379b7fd3f06.avif?t=1771010071\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867320/extras_big/d8d2eaf43adbd2b921912379b7fd3f06.avif?t=1771010071 width=800 height=266 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867320/extras/5c8cd32ba3d543044d041dfe013804fb.webp?t=1771010071\" width=188 height=42 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience over<strong> 200 roles</strong>, each offering distinct abilities and win conditions, and support for <strong>community roles</strong> and <strong>sets</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >‎ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >‎ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867320/extras/f5a942dea5fe98b176ffe1657b2399c3.avif?t=1771010071\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867320/extras_big/f5a942dea5fe98b176ffe1657b2399c3.avif?t=1771010071 width=800 height=266 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867320/extras/c3816d94a82a96a1aedc69f73701675e.webp?t=1771010071\" width=346 height=42 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Express yourself with deep <strong>character customization</strong>! Personalize your character with a vast array of clothes, armor, accessories, and hairstyles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\t‎ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >‎ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867320/extras/e38434de758694d267fd3a14422d9a19.avif?t=1771010071\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867320/extras_big/e38434de758694d267fd3a14422d9a19.avif?t=1771010071 width=800 height=266 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867320/extras/2d0bc4ae38b48960625bd6027b09887d.webp?t=1771010071\" width=268 height=42 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\tExplore a multitude of <strong>detailed and atmospheric locations. </strong>Including a bustling<strong> Tavern,</strong> a once secure <strong>Village</strong> now threatened by Werewolves,<strong> </strong>the eerie depths of the <strong>Werewolf Cave</strong>, and many more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >‎ </p>",
